description._content: Bain News Service,, publisher. Gen. von Kessel 1914 Dec. 11 (date created or published later by Bain) 1 negative : glass ; 5 x 7 in. or smaller. Notes: Title and date from data provided by the Bain News Service on the negative. Photograph shows General Emil Bernhard Bodo von Kessell (1846-1918), a German military officer who served in World War I. (Source: Flickr Commons project, 2011) Forms part of: George Grantham Bain Collection (Library of Congress). Format: Glass negatives. Rights Info: No known restrictions on publication.
